<Body><Title>四平铁东区一店铺发生火灾 4人被困火海</Title>
<ReportTime type="absTime">2014-03-31 19:47　</ReportTime>来源: 新文化网
<Content><Paragraph>
<Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Time type="relTime" tid="t1">3月29日6时57分</Time>，<Participant sid="s1">四平市公安消防支队特勤消防</Participant><Denoter type="action" did="d1">接到</Denoter><Object oid="o1">119指挥中心调度命令</Object></Event>：
<Event eid="e2"><Location lid="l2">位于铁东区南一纬七马路一家水暖件店铺</Location>发生<Denoter type="emergency" did="d2">火灾</Denoter></Event>，有人员被困。</Sentence><Sentence>
<Event eid="e3"><Denoter type="action" did="d3">接到</Denoter><Object oid="o3">报警</Object></Event>后，
<Event eid="e4"><Participant sid="s4">中队</Participant>迅速<Denoter type="action" did="d4">出动</Denoter><Object oid="o4">辆水罐消防车、1辆器材消防车、</Object><Participant oid="o4">320名指战员</Participant></Event>
<Event eid="e5"><Denoter type="movement" did="d5">赶赴</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l5">火灾现场</Location></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>


　　<Paragraph><Sentence>
<Event eid="e6">经过<Time type="timeInterval" tid="t6">5分钟</Time>全力<Denoter type="operation" did="d6">救援</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e7"><Participant  oid="o7">4名被困人员</Participant>被全部<Denoter type="operation" did="d7">救出</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e8">并<Denoter type="movement" did="d8">转移</Denoter>到<Location type="destination" lid="l8">安全地带</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e9">同时<Object oid="o9">火势</Object>得到了有效<Denoter type="operation" did="d9">控制</Denoter></Event>；<Event eid="e10">经过<Time type="timeInterval" tid="t10">10分钟</Time>的奋力<Denoter type="operation" did="d10">扑救</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Object oid="o11">大火</Object>被<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d11">扑灭</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence>为确保安全，指挥员根据现场情况对起火部位及其周围实施了冷却降温，防止发生复燃。7时40分，在确保现场无复燃可能后，中队官兵移交现场后，收整器材归队。</Sentence>

</Paragraph></Content>
